        {
            "title": "比亞迪溢利跌近19%  末期息35.8分",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">比亞迪(01211)公布，截至2025年12月31日母公司持有人應佔溢利329.19億元，按年倒退18.97%，基本每股收益3.58元，2024年同期4.61元。派末期息每股35.8分，較2024年末期息3.974元跌90.99%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/c2fe8ed6647f245161b7648cd7407a51_China_BYD_414_8.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/c2fe8ed6647f245161b7648cd7407a51_China_BYD_414_8.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">這是自2021年以來首錄全年盈利倒退。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">毛利1,426.6億元，下降5.6%，毛利率由19.44%降至17.74%。全年研發投入634億元，上升17%，累計研發投入超2,400億元。營業額8039.65億元，按年升3.46%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">單計第四季，盈利下跌38%，至93億元，營業額下降14%至2377億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15810360-%e6%af%94%e4%ba%9e%e8%bf%aa%e6%ba%a2%e5%88%a9%e8%b7%8c%e8%bf%9119-%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af35-8%e5%88%86",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250704_FI_source-ap_01211-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-30 08:55:00",
